fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.examples.ssqueue

Class Client

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.examples.ssqueue.Client
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EventInformationI, java.io.Serializable

    public class Client
extends java.lang.Object
implements EventInformationI
    The class Client defines a simple client in a simulation of a single server queue model M/M/1.

    Description

    The client object will hold its arrival time that will be used when finishing its service to compute its sojourn time (waiting plus service).

    Invariant

     invariant              true

    Created on : 2018-07-11

    Author:
    Jacques Malenfant
